{"type": "article", "id": 5962, "title": "Fungi Shelves 搁架", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-06T07:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233905uYrfORp0TQ8tASE4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tGridy 是一对设计师组合，Fungi Shelves 是他们为丹麦家居品牌 Menu 带来的全新搁架作品，其设计灵感源自大自然的一个古怪的特性，就像是从森林树木上水平长出来的真菌一样。不管是将其用在起居室、卧室、厨房还是卫生间，都有用武之地，而这两位挪威设计师的愿望也就是创造这样简单实用却又充满强烈个性的作品。提供黑色、深橡木与浅橡木 3 种颜色与大中小三种型号选择，定价 299.95 丹麦克朗（约合人民币 288 元），<a href=\"http://menu.as/shop/furniture/shelving/gridy-fungi-shelf-small-natural-oak\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233903qSgjeV4GOmi81BDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233904kRLKM54Os0xhaYvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233904ejHCJFZ3sBycSPMa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}